summary: Onboarding with rendezvous started late (device retries then succeeds)
description: |
    Sets up manufacturer and owner, leaves rendezvous stopped initially.
    Confirms device onboarding attempts fail (not found / rendezvous unavailable),
    then starts rendezvous and verifies TO0 completes and onboarding succeeds.

test: ../../rpm/test-onboarding-deferred-rendezvous.sh

framework: shell

duration: 30m

require:
  - go-fdo-server
  - go-fdo-server-manufacturer
  - go-fdo-server-owner
  - go-fdo-server-rendezvous

tag:
  - fdo
  - e2e
  - protocol
  - onboarding
  - rendezvous
  - deferred
  - rpm
  - server
